{"tid":748123,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"(Unity)又係我unity大傻鳩，想問點樣set array入playerprefs到","createTime":"2018-07-19T03:19:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-21T03:02:06.000Z","uid":5963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"45bf16c86b412ea44542b8fe4886e9ee00a0f9bd","tid":748123,"uid":5963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T03:19:47.000Z","msg":"是咁點，我最近整緊個扭蛋系統去解鎖一d車，但因為每次重開game d 車又會全部上鎖晒，我想用set去save低一個int array，之後void start去get個數，如果int = 1，咁車既active就會係true，但我唔知一get完之後點先可以拎返個數黎用<br />\n<br />\nint R;<br />\nint truefalse[];<br />\nGameObject Cars[];<br />\n<br />\nvoid Generate()<br />\n{<br />\n<br />\nR=Random.Range(0, Car.Length);<br />\ntruefalse[R]=1;<br />\nif (truefalse[R]=1)<br />\n{<br />\n<br />\nGameObject Cars[R].SetActive(true);<br />\n<br />\n}<br />\n<br />\n}<br />\n<br />\n未加get set既時侯大概係咁，dllm都整左四日，我真係好撚豬閪，試過用playerprefsX，但都係拎唔到個數出黎，或者講我自己唔識用"},{"pid":"82edf1eba43cac1e0b2c13f523bd3b1f389f55f9","tid":748123,"uid":42469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T06:55:37.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">List&lt;int&gt; CarsId;\nList&lt;bool&gt; CarsUnlocked;\n\nfor (int i = 0; i &lt; NumberOfCars; i++) {\nPlayerPrefs.SetInt(CarsId[i].ToString(), CarsUnlocked[i] ? 1 : 0 );\n}\nPlayerPrefs.Save();</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n拎返就翻轉寫<br />\n利申未用過，即刻Google only"},{"pid":"9b810fe4a7e3c11b32fa9c2d696d7101177cb7b1","tid":748123,"uid":33875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T09:35:39.000Z","msg":"又係你，留個ig比你問<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d2959a50e1aca0dc9ed6849aab82499bb650ad7","tid":748123,"uid":5963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b810fe4a7e3c11b32fa9c2d696d7101177cb7b1","tid":748123,"uid":33875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T09:35:39.000Z","msg":"又係你，留個ig比你問<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"cite